{
  "id": "rss-harvester",
  "name": "RSS Harvester",
  "tagline": "Polls RSS and Atom feeds on a schedule and publishes news.article items to the Item Bus.",
  "description": "A producer worker that fetches one or more RSS/Atom feed URLs on a configurable schedule and pushes each new entry as a `news.article` item onto the BFrost Item Bus. Deduplication is keyed on the entry's `<link>` element — an article is only published once per source URL.\n\nFeed URLs are declared in worker settings as a newline-separated list. Supports both RSS 2.0 and Atom 1.0.",
